Invocation Name: knock out
des:
A customized boxing trainer for beginners. Boxing, is an unarmed combat sport, and has it's history as early as 1500 BC. Boxing is special, because it is not only a hobby that you can learn, but also, a tiring sport, a fitness regimen, and also a highly successful form of self defence.
It helps you to learn discipline, self control, and gain enormous self confidence with regular practice. To customize your experience, we have 2 trainers, Mike, and Laila, whom you can choose to train with.
